query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathematica',
'security',
'wordpress')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('admin',
'attacks',
'css',
'error',
'evaluation',
'mobile',
'output-formatting',
'pattern-matching',
'post-thumbnails',
'taxonomy',
'uploads',
'users',
'widgets')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Guru',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
